 *   and ComponentStorage before driving the spatial index.
 * - @ref tutorial_combat — Combat relies on spatial queries to
 *   find AoE targets and aggro lists.
 * - @ref tutorial_ai_behavior — AI uses `QueryRadius` inside
 *   BTAction nodes to pick targets.
 * - `advanced/ECS_DEEP_DIVE.md` — System parallelism and
 *   dependency scheduling.
 * - `include/cgs/game/spatial_index.hpp` — authoritative API.
 * - `include/cgs/game/world_types.hpp` — full `ZoneFlags` enum.
 */
